headline: 3 Crucial Things Investors Should Do During the Nasdaq Correction
summary: The tech-heavy Nasdaq Composite stock index has been one of the big winners of the artificial intelligence (AI) boom.  The benchmark roared higher over the past two years, posting consecutive double-digit gains, as investors piled into players present in this hot growth area.  President Donald Trump recently launched tariffs on imports from China, Canada, and Mexico -- a move to protest the flow of lethal drugs and illegal immigrants across borders and into the U.S., the Trump administration says.
